quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Dumisa igama leNkosi yakho ephakeme kakhulu
  87,2,Okuyiyona eyadala yalinganisa (konke ngesimo sako)
  87,3,Futhi okuyiyona ekalayo futhi eholayo
  87,4,Futhi okuyiyona eyaveza okuluhlaza (utshani nezihlahla)
  87,5,Yabe seyikwenza kwaba yizinhlanga ezinsundu
  87,6,Sizokwenza ukuthi ufunde angeke ukhohlwe
  87,7,"Ngaphandle kwalokho okufiswa nguMvelinqangi, ngempela yena uyakwazi okusobala kanye nalokho okufihlekile"
  87,8,Futhi sikwenzela kubelula okulula
  87,9,"Ngakho-ke\tkhumbuza\tuma\tkungukuthi\tsiyakusiza isikhumbuzo"
  87,10,Uyokhumbula lowo owesaba (uMvelinqangi)
  87,11,Futhi uyokugwema (ukukhunjuzwa) lowo muntu omubi kakhulu
  87,12,Lowo uzokusha emlilweni omkhulu
  87,13,Bese engafi lapho phakathi kuwona futhi angaphili
  87,14,Ngempela uphumelele lowo ozihlanzayo
  87,15,Futhi akhumbule igama leNkosi yakhe athandaze
  87,16,Kepha nikhetha impilo yalomhlaba
  87,17,Futhi impilo ezayo ingcono futhi ingehlalayo engapheliyo
  87,18,Ngempela lokhu kusemibhalweni yokuqala
  87,19,Imibhalo ka-Abrahamu noMose